data.description: Rare Tennis/Equestrian Estate in beautiful Garner Valley with panoramic views of the San Jacinto Mountain range. From the stately entry you step in to the Great Room with dramatic wall of windows encased in stone and the unobstructed view of the mountains beyond.The open beam ceiling and stone floors compliment this unique home. The main floor master suite features a fireplace, walk-in closet, glass doors opening unto the deck and hot tub,dual vanities and heated stone floor in the master bath along with a walk-in shower and spa tub. Upstairs master suite overlooks the great room with 3/4 bath. Along with the professional tennis court, gardens and hot house the grounds have room for extensive equestrian facilities. The huge deck is perfect for entertaining and watching a game of tennis in the cool mountain air.
